{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":968,"text":"I moved to Boston\n10 years ago from Chicago,"},{"time":4285,"text":"with an interest in cancer\nand in chemistry."},{"time":7373,"text":"You might know that chemistry\nis the science of making molecules"},{"time":10692,"text":"or, to my taste,"},{"time":12032,"text":"new drugs for cancer."},{"time":14179,"text":"And you might also know that,\nfor science and medicine,"},{"time":17000,"text":"Boston is a bit of a candy store."},{"time":20507,"text":"You can't roll a stop sign in Cambridge\nwithout hitting a graduate student."},{"time":25154,"text":"The bar is called the Miracle of Science."},{"time":27733,"text":"The billboards say \"Lab Space Available.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":31396,"text":"And it's fair to say\nthat in these 10 years,"},{"time":33579,"text":"we've witnessed absolutely the start\nof a scientific revolution --"},{"time":37910,"text":"that of genome medicine."},{"time":39775,"text":"We know more about the patients\nthat enter our clinic now"},{"time":42529,"text":"than ever before."},{"time":43712,"text":"And we're able, finally,\nto answer the question"},{"time":45960,"text":"that's been so pressing for so many years:"},{"time":48348,"text":"Why do I have cancer?"},{"time":51415,"text":"This information\nis also pretty staggering."},{"time":53955,"text":"You might know that, so far,\nin just the dawn of this revolution,"},{"time":57072,"text":"we know that there are perhaps\n40,000 unique mutations"},{"time":60822,"text":"affecting more than 10,000 genes,"},{"time":63457,"text":"and that there are 500 of these genes\nthat are bona-fide drivers,"},{"time":66844,"text":"causes of cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69834,"text":"Yet comparatively,"},{"time":71053,"text":"we have about a dozen\ntargeted medications."},{"time":74712,"text":"And this inadequacy of cancer medicine"},{"time":76998,"text":"really hit home when my father\nwas diagnosed with pancreatic cancer."},{"time":82950,"text":"We didn't fly him to Boston."},{"time":84635,"text":"We didn't sequence his genome."},{"time":86547,"text":"It's been known for decades\nwhat causes this malignancy."},{"time":91103,"text":"It's three proteins: ras, myc, p53."},{"time":95677,"text":"This is old information\nwe've known since about the 80s,"},{"time":98399,"text":"yet there's no medicine I can prescribe"},{"time":100343,"text":"to a patient with this\nor any of the numerous solid tumors"},{"time":103930,"text":"caused by these three ..."},{"time":106581,"text":"Horsemen of the Apocalypse that is cancer."},{"time":109279,"text":"There's no ras, no myc, no p53 drug."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112096,"text":"And you might fairly ask: Why is that?"},{"time":115049,"text":"And the very unsatisfying\nyet scientific answer is:"},{"time":117906,"text":"it's too hard."},{"time":119620,"text":"That for whatever reason,"},{"time":120914,"text":"these three proteins have entered\na space, in the language of our field,"},{"time":124431,"text":"that's called the undruggable genome --"},{"time":126655,"text":"which is like calling\na computer unsurfable"},{"time":128969,"text":"or the Moon unwalkable."},{"time":130249,"text":"It's a horrible term of trade."},{"time":132381,"text":"But what it means"},{"time":133563,"text":"is that we've failed to identify\na greasy pocket in these proteins,"},{"time":136809,"text":"into which we, like molecular locksmiths,"},{"time":139103,"text":"can fashion an active, small,\norganic molecule or drug substance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144774,"text":"Now, as I was training\nin clinical medicine"},{"time":147231,"text":"and hematology and oncology\nand stem-cell transplantation,"},{"time":150716,"text":"what we had instead,"},{"time":152613,"text":"cascading through the regulatory\nnetwork at the FDA,"},{"time":156152,"text":"were these substances:"},{"time":157609,"text":"arsenic,"},{"time":158942,"text":"thalidomide,"},{"time":160131,"text":"and this chemical derivative\nof nitrogen mustard gas."},{"time":163512,"text":"And this is the 21st century."},{"time":166145,"text":"And so, I guess you'd say,"},{"time":167415,"text":"dissatisfied with the performance\nand quality of these medicines,"},{"time":170576,"text":"I went back to school, in chemistry,"},{"time":174049,"text":"with the idea that perhaps by learning\nthe trade of discovery chemistry"},{"time":178732,"text":"and approaching it in the context\nof this brave new world"},{"time":181629,"text":"of the open source,"},{"time":183865,"text":"the crowd source,"},{"time":185317,"text":"the collaborative network\nthat we have access to within academia,"},{"time":188646,"text":"that we might more quickly bring\npowerful and targeted therapies"},{"time":192948,"text":"to our patients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194691,"text":"And so, please consider\nthis a work in progress,"},{"time":197815,"text":"but I'd like to tell you today a story"},{"time":199856,"text":"about a very rare cancer\ncalled midline carcinoma,"},{"time":203859,"text":"about the undruggable protein target\nthat causes this cancer,"},{"time":208097,"text":"called BRD4,"},{"time":209649,"text":"and about a molecule developed at my lab\nat Dana-Farber Cancer Institute,"},{"time":213518,"text":"called JQ1,"},{"time":214694,"text":"which we affectionately named for Jun Qi,"},{"time":216940,"text":"the chemist that made this molecule."},{"time":219709,"text":"Now, BRD4 is an interesting protein."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222429,"text":"You might ask: with all the things\ncancer's trying to do to kill our patient,"},{"time":226134,"text":"how does it remember it's cancer?"},{"time":227746,"text":"When it winds up its genome,"},{"time":229201,"text":"divides into two cells and unwinds again,"},{"time":231596,"text":"why does it not turn\ninto an eye, into a liver,"},{"time":233857,"text":"as it has all the genes\nnecessary to do this?"},{"time":236262,"text":"It remembers that it's cancer."},{"time":238688,"text":"And the reason is that cancer,\nlike every cell in the body,"},{"time":241800,"text":"places little molecular bookmarks,"},{"time":243800,"text":"little Post-it notes,"},{"time":245202,"text":"that remind the cell, \"I'm cancer;\nI should keep growing.\""},{"time":248800,"text":"And those Post-it notes involve this\nand other proteins of its class --"},{"time":252837,"text":"so-called bromodomains."},{"time":254732,"text":"So we developed an idea, a rationale,"},{"time":257424,"text":"that perhaps if we made a molecule"},{"time":259597,"text":"that prevented\nthe Post-it note from sticking"},{"time":261914,"text":"by entering into the little pocket"},{"time":263597,"text":"at the base of this spinning protein,"},{"time":265477,"text":"then maybe we could convince cancer cells,"},{"time":267557,"text":"certainly those addicted\nto this BRD4 protein,"},{"time":270382,"text":"that they're not cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272418,"text":"And so we started to work on this problem."},{"time":274665,"text":"We developed libraries of compounds"},{"time":276991,"text":"and eventually arrived\nat this and similar substances"},{"time":279800,"text":"called JQ1."},{"time":281577,"text":"Now, not being a drug company,"},{"time":283165,"text":"we could do certain things,\nwe had certain flexibilities,"},{"time":286283,"text":"that I respect that a pharmaceutical\nindustry doesn't have."},{"time":289141,"text":"We just started mailing it to our friends."},{"time":291883,"text":"I have a small lab."},{"time":293060,"text":"We thought we'd just send it to people\nand see how the molecule behaves."},{"time":296489,"text":"We sent it to Oxford, England,"},{"time":297963,"text":"where a group of talented\ncrystallographers provided this picture,"},{"time":301209,"text":"which helped us understand exactly\nhow this molecule is so potent"},{"time":304330,"text":"for this protein target."},{"time":305520,"text":"It's what we call a perfect fit\nof shape complementarity,"},{"time":308480,"text":"or hand in glove."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310327,"text":"Now, this is a very rare cancer,"},{"time":311972,"text":"this BRD4-addicted cancer."},{"time":314201,"text":"And so we worked with samples of material"},{"time":316456,"text":"that were collected by young pathologists\nat Brigham and Women's Hospital."},{"time":320054,"text":"And as we treated these cells\nwith this molecule,"},{"time":322451,"text":"we observed something really striking."},{"time":324800,"text":"The cancer cells --"},{"time":326030,"text":"small, round and rapidly dividing,"},{"time":328121,"text":"grew these arms and extensions."},{"time":330498,"text":"They were changing shape."},{"time":332320,"text":"In effect,"},{"time":333671,"text":"the cancer cell\nwas forgetting it was cancer"},{"time":337002,"text":"and becoming a normal cell."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340076,"text":"This got us very excited."},{"time":342841,"text":"The next step would be to put\nthis molecule into mice."},{"time":345453,"text":"The only problem was there's no\nmouse model of this rare cancer."},{"time":348872,"text":"And so at the time\nwe were doing this research,"},{"time":351619,"text":"I was caring for a 29-year-old\nfirefighter from Connecticut"},{"time":355216,"text":"who was very much at the end of life"},{"time":357122,"text":"with this incurable cancer."},{"time":359621,"text":"This BRD4-addicted cancer\nwas growing throughout his left lung."},{"time":363095,"text":"And he had a chest tube in\nthat was draining little bits of debris."},{"time":366284,"text":"And every nursing shift,\nwe would throw this material out."},{"time":369269,"text":"And so we approached this patient"},{"time":371060,"text":"and asked if he would collaborate with us."},{"time":373715,"text":"Could we take this precious\nand rare cancerous material"},{"time":377438,"text":"from this chest tube"},{"time":379061,"text":"and drive it across town\nand put it into mice"},{"time":381304,"text":"and try to do a clinical trial\nat a stage that with a prototype drug,"},{"time":384969,"text":"well, that would be, of course, impossible"},{"time":387017,"text":"and, rightly, illegal to do in humans."},{"time":388874,"text":"And he obliged us."},{"time":391006,"text":"At the Lurie Family Center\nfor Animal Imaging,"},{"time":393222,"text":"our colleague, Andrew Kung,\ngrew this cancer successfully in mice"},{"time":396861,"text":"without ever touching plastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398575,"text":"And you can see this PET scan\nof a mouse -- what we call a pet PET."},{"time":402015,"text":"The cancer is growing"},{"time":403595,"text":"as this red, huge mass\nin the hind limb of this animal."},{"time":406921,"text":"And as we treat it with our compound,"},{"time":409168,"text":"this addiction to sugar,"},{"time":410800,"text":"this rapid growth, faded."},{"time":412415,"text":"And on the animal on the right,"},{"time":414482,"text":"you see that the cancer was responding."},{"time":417569,"text":"We've completed, now, clinical trials"},{"time":419800,"text":"in four mouse models of this disease."},{"time":421800,"text":"And every time, we see the same thing."},{"time":423673,"text":"The mice with this cancer\nthat get the drug live,"},{"time":426402,"text":"and the ones that don't rapidly perish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430800,"text":"So we started to wonder,"},{"time":432253,"text":"what would a drug company\ndo at this point?"},{"time":434381,"text":"Well, they probably\nwould keep this a secret"},{"time":436454,"text":"until they turn the prototype drug"},{"time":438363,"text":"into an active pharmaceutical substance."},{"time":441063,"text":"So we did just the opposite."},{"time":442884,"text":"We published a paper\nthat described this finding"},{"time":445743,"text":"at the earliest prototype stage."},{"time":448513,"text":"We gave the world the chemical\nidentity of this molecule,"},{"time":451445,"text":"typically a secret in our discipline."},{"time":453366,"text":"We told people exactly how to make it."},{"time":456039,"text":"We gave them our email address,"},{"time":457731,"text":"suggesting that if they write us,"},{"time":459406,"text":"we'll send them a free molecule."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461032,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462144,"text":"We basically tried to create\nthe most competitive environment"},{"time":465065,"text":"for our lab as possible."},{"time":466249,"text":"And this was, unfortunately, successful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468215,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":469263,"text":"Because now, we've shared this molecule,"},{"time":471292,"text":"just since December of last year,"},{"time":473719,"text":"with 40 laboratories in the United States"},{"time":475998,"text":"and 30 more in Europe --"},{"time":477800,"text":"many of them pharmaceutical companies,"},{"time":479673,"text":"seeking now to enter this space,"},{"time":481292,"text":"to target this rare cancer\nthat, thankfully right now,"},{"time":485196,"text":"is quite desirable\nto study in that industry."},{"time":490062,"text":"But the science that's coming back\nfrom all of these laboratories"},{"time":493155,"text":"about the use of this molecule"},{"time":495013,"text":"has provided us insights\nwe might not have had on our own."},{"time":498210,"text":"Leukemia cells treated with this compound"},{"time":500211,"text":"turn into normal white blood cells."},{"time":503276,"text":"Mice with multiple myeloma,"},{"time":505081,"text":"an incurable malignancy\nof the bone marrow,"},{"time":508140,"text":"respond dramatically"},{"time":510141,"text":"to the treatment with this drug."},{"time":512316,"text":"You might know that fat has memory."},{"time":515364,"text":"I'll nicely demonstrate that for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517364,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":518419,"text":"In fact, this molecule"},{"time":519995,"text":"prevents this adipocyte,\nthis fat stem cell,"},{"time":523419,"text":"from remembering how to make fat,"},{"time":526312,"text":"such that mice on a high-fat diet,"},{"time":528704,"text":"like the folks\nin my hometown of Chicago --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":530842,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531874,"text":"fail to develop fatty liver,"},{"time":533906,"text":"which is a major medical problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536920,"text":"What this research taught us --"},{"time":538516,"text":"not just my lab, but our institute,"},{"time":540800,"text":"and Harvard Medical School\nmore generally --"},{"time":542896,"text":"is that we have unique\nresources in academia"},{"time":545181,"text":"for drug discovery;"},{"time":546539,"text":"that our center, which has tested\nperhaps more cancer molecules"},{"time":549746,"text":"in a scientific way"},{"time":550927,"text":"than any other,"},{"time":552102,"text":"never made one of its own."},{"time":554545,"text":"For all the reasons you see listed here,"},{"time":556736,"text":"we think there's a great\nopportunity for academic centers"},{"time":559499,"text":"to participate in this earliest,\nconceptually tricky"},{"time":563347,"text":"and creative discipline"},{"time":565301,"text":"of prototype drug discovery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569872,"text":"So what next?"},{"time":571349,"text":"We have this molecule,\nbut it's not a pill yet."},{"time":573753,"text":"It's not orally bioavailable."},{"time":576371,"text":"We need to fix it so we can\ndeliver it to our patients."},{"time":579590,"text":"And everyone in the lab,"},{"time":581198,"text":"especially following the interaction\nwith these patients,"},{"time":584023,"text":"feels quite compelled\nto deliver a drug substance"},{"time":586372,"text":"based on this molecule."},{"time":587594,"text":"It's here where I'd say"},{"time":589029,"text":"that we could use your help\nand your insights,"},{"time":591268,"text":"your collaborative participation."},{"time":593481,"text":"Unlike a drug company,\nwe don't have a pipeline"},{"time":597186,"text":"that we can deposit these molecules into."},{"time":599217,"text":"We don't have a team\nof salespeople and marketeers"},{"time":601638,"text":"to tell us how to position\nthis drug against the other."},{"time":604373,"text":"What we do have is the flexibility\nof an academic center"},{"time":607065,"text":"to work with competent, motivated,"},{"time":609441,"text":"enthusiastic, hopefully well-funded people"},{"time":612370,"text":"to carry these molecules\nforward into the clinic"},{"time":614687,"text":"while preserving our ability\nto share the prototype drug worldwide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619474,"text":"This molecule will soon leave our benches"},{"time":622139,"text":"and go into a small start-up company\ncalled Tensha Therapeutics."},{"time":625213,"text":"And, really, this is the fourth\nof these molecules"},{"time":628173,"text":"to kind of \"graduate\"\nfrom our little pipeline"},{"time":630444,"text":"of drug discovery,"},{"time":631922,"text":"two of which -- a topical drug\nfor lymphoma of the skin"},{"time":637197,"text":"and an oral substance for the treatment\nof multiple myeloma --"},{"time":640332,"text":"will actually come to the bedside\nfor the first clinical trial"},{"time":643594,"text":"in July of this year -- for us,\na major and exciting milestone."},{"time":648649,"text":"I want to leave you with just two ideas."},{"time":650696,"text":"The first is: if anything is unique\nabout this research,"},{"time":655054,"text":"it's less the science than the strategy."},{"time":657435,"text":"This, for us, was a social experiment --"},{"time":659881,"text":"an experiment in \"What would happen\nif we were as open and honest"},{"time":665170,"text":"at the earliest phase\nof discovery chemistry research"},{"time":667710,"text":"as we could be?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":669181,"text":"This string of letters and numbers"},{"time":671546,"text":"and symbols and parentheses"},{"time":673585,"text":"that can be texted, I suppose,"},{"time":675228,"text":"or Twittered worldwide,"},{"time":677948,"text":"is the chemical identity\nof our pro compound."},{"time":680474,"text":"It's the information that we most need\nfrom pharmaceutical companies,"},{"time":684580,"text":"the information on how these early\nprototype drugs might work."},{"time":689688,"text":"Yet this information is largely a secret."},{"time":692482,"text":"And so we seek, really, to download"},{"time":695385,"text":"from the amazing successes\nof the computer-science industry,"},{"time":698528,"text":"two principles -- that of open source\nand that of crowdsourcing --"},{"time":702931,"text":"to quickly, responsibly accelerate\nthe delivery of targeted therapeutics"},{"time":708949,"text":"to patients with cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711117,"text":"Now, the business model\ninvolves all of you."},{"time":714260,"text":"This research is funded by the public."},{"time":716585,"text":"It's funded by foundations."},{"time":717987,"text":"And one thing I've learned in Boston"},{"time":719741,"text":"is that you people will do anything\nfor cancer, and I love that."},{"time":722839,"text":"You bike across the state,\nyou walk up and down the river."}]},{"cues":[{"time":725760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":727890,"text":"I've never seen, really, anywhere,"},{"time":730240,"text":"this unique support for cancer research."},{"time":733507,"text":"And so I want to thank you"},{"time":735288,"text":"for your participation, your collaboration"},{"time":738609,"text":"and most of all,"},{"time":739794,"text":"for your confidence in our ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741752,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}